room_title: Escape room "The Rescue of Professor Dawkins" by Minute 59 Mystery and Escape Rooms in Bemidji
room_address: 802 Paul Bunyan Dr SE #17, Bemidji, MN 56601
room_description: A madman is attempting to take possession of the country as his own personal kingdom by using a mind control machine. Your mentor has built an apparatus to prevent this, but he has been kidnapped. You must get the apparatus working to stop evil from taking over the country and save Professor Dawkins. He is counting on your help!
